passes.benefit_text:
Admits 50% off up to 4 ferry tickets from Boston to Spectacle Island and Georges Island, or from Hingham to Peddocks Island.&nbsp;
This is a SEASONAL pass available mid-May through early October.
Please CHECK SCHEDULE on website before booking. Not all islands are open every day.&nbsp;
Specific dates and islands for the current 2026 season are at&nbsp;
https://www.bostonharborislands.org/ferryschedule/
